13 March 2014Members of the media are invited to a post State of Nation Address (SoNA) media briefing on Local Government. Minister of Cooperative Governance and Traditional Affairs, Lechesa Tsenoli will lead the media briefing. Details are as follows: Date: 14 March 2014 Time: 10h00 Venue: GCIS media briefing room, Tshedimosetso House, 1035 Francis Baard, Corner Festival Street, Hatfield, Pretoria NB: There will be a video-link to Imbizo Media Centre, Cape Town, Parliament RSVP: Ireen Magwai (Pretoria) Cell: 072 822 5869 E-mail:ireen@gcis.gov.za Mzimasi Ngqelu (Cape Town) Cell: 076 904 3557 E-mail: mzi@gcis.gov.za Enquiries: Tsakane Baloyi 082 052 0892Issued by Government Communication and Information System